|    6 | fida     | mahi         | 1998 |     2344 |
|    7 | maanas   | thamarassery | 1999 |     4567 |
|    8 | ashwathi | vadakara     | 1996 |     2347 |
|    9 | aswin    | omassery     | 1999 |     2587 |
+------+----------+--------------+------+----------+
